Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(350,345)\fs19}第75層  科力尼亞  轉移門廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「怎麼」是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是擱下了生意前來支援你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解我這種無私無慾的精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼分配戰利品的時候就把你排除在外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴廊開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有種不詳的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由血盟騎士團在前排頂住BOSS的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位能趁此機會盡可能地看清攻擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況進行反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這會是場艱苦的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信以諸位的力量是能夠戰勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了解放的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人君也要守護我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不大撈一筆戰利品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不會倒下的
