Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人同時接招的話  能擋住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的話一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐮刀由我們來擋住
